        Property Styling vs Renovation Before Selling in Brisbane: Which Is Worth It?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Sellers in Brisbane's inner east often spend too much in the wrong places before listing. Here is where the return actually is, and what is better left alone.
      </p>
